    "BravyiUnitary[r] represents the Gaussian-type unitary operator that \
transforms 2 n Majorana fermion modes according to 2 n*2 n orthogonal matrix \
r := MatrixExp[a] associated with a 2 n*2 n anti-symmetric matrix a. \
BravyiUnitary[{1, n}] is equivalent to BravyiUnitary[I 2 n*2 n].", 
    "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "BravyiUnitary", 
